texts.mesg:
Hey there beetle!
Use your W, A, S, and D keys to move around.
Press the W key to jump and collect candy corn.

First, press S to crouch.
Then, press W to HIGH JUMP
BEETLE JUICE will make you faster.

Use your WASD keys
to control BOUNCY BEETLE

Hold down the W key
to become EXTRA BOUNCY

Use your WASD keys
to fly HOVER BEETLE

As STICKY BEETLE, use your mouse
to CLICK in the direction
you want to go.

TUTORIAL COMPLETE.
Press Pause (in the upper right corner)
to return to the menu.
